Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:19.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも踊りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:29.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,眠れないくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:37.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,情熱の火はいつしか　いつの日にか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はなから気付いている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,炎はいつか消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何も要らないはずだった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:49.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なのにまだ I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:54.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ　まだ間に合う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:01:00.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ ただ Burn it up Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling そんなに甘くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもきっとそんなに悪くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:09.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ Give me fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:12.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Light it up Baby 燃やしちゃうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:32.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:35.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:37.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああただBurn it up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:40.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:44.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Light it up Baby 燃やしちゃうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:48.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,#5 The story of the Moriko Song, part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:18.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:22.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここでもダメなのかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:31.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,静かすぎて怖いくらいだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:50.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは百鬼丸が取り戻したどの感覚よりも衝撃だった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:53.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,容赦なく頭の中に入り込んでくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:57.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無数の振動の取捨選択など、できるはずもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:02.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸はただ音の洪水に溺れていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:08.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、やっぱり今回のあやかし退治はやめとこうか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:12.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,礼金いいから勿体ねぇけど、こんな調子じゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:16.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出たのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来た！鳥のあやかし、でけぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！音なんか気にすんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,左だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:10.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:35.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おや 坊やたちだったかい 奇遇だねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき あにき？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:41.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しっかりしてくれよ！あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:49.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:59.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうかい、耳がねぇ。そいつはよかったじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくなんかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞こえるようになったせいであにき、弱くなちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:05.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:11.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だって、坊さんでもあんな簡単にやっつけられる\Nあやかしにこんなにやられちまってさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつはごあいさつだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ…あにき、大丈夫だよな…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急場は凌いだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当なら薬が欲しいとこじゃあるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:26.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、ひとっ走り行ってこようか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,川向こうに大きな町があるはずだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:33.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,およし どうやら戦がありそうだからね 危ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:39.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この辺りを治める酒井って武将が 同盟国を裏切ったとかでね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,2つの軍が睨み合いさね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:47.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなとこにあたしらみたいなよそ者が近づくのは剣呑だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,で、引き返してきたとこにさっきの騒ぎってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:55.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くそっ！武士ってのはなんでそんなに戦が好きなんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…うるさかったか、ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,動くんじゃないよ 傷が開いちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,穴ぐらに籠もった手負いの獣ってとこだね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:15.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいかい？これは人の声だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:19.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,周りにあるのは、森に生きてるモンや火や風の音さ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さんは慣れなきゃいけないよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,穴ぐらからこの世に出るためにはね！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怪我人なんだぞ？無理させんなって！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきはまだ仏さんになるわけにはいかねぇんだからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんともしんとした声だねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ動いちゃ危ないよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やれやれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,…こんな固いの食えねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,花　あかい花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:29.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人の髪に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:37.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,咲いてゆれるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お陽さまの…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怪我してるの？大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ、見えてないのね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら、ここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,熱があるんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:12.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんな水の中に入っちゃダメ 早く出て！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょっと、しっかりして！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんなに弱っちまってるあにき、初めてだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ怪我のせいもあるだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神からいろんなモン取り戻したようだからねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,頭がおっつかないのかもしれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これ、古着解いたのだけど綺麗だから使って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオさん…だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:56.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,邪魔しちまったうえに面倒かけて悪いねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:09:00.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなこと…治るまでいてもらって大丈夫だから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:07.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もちろん ここには、あんたの兄さんみたいな子もたくさんいるから 安心して
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みんな慣れてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:13.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みんな！こそこそしないで、ちゃんと挨拶しなさい！ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひどい戦があってね…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:31.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,家も何も、全部なくなってしまって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな者同士集まって暮らしてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃあ、みんなおとちゃんもおかちゃんも…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そ　でも、みんないい子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子供ばかりだって、なんとかなるもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:48.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あー、ミオ姉！まだ起きてんのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら、どいたどいた！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:56.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉、今のうちに寝とかねぇと身体もたねぇぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怪我人は俺が面倒見っから、早く寝ろって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかったわかった！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:04.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃ、何かあったらこのタケ坊に聞いて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:08.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早く！朝メシ用意してあるから ちゃんと食ってから寝るんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はいはい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:12.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たちの朝メシもある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,芋粥だ 食え
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ど…どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんか手伝うことねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいって お前は怪我人見てろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:39.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや、タダで世話になるわけにはいかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:42.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,メシ代ぐらいは働くのが筋ってもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほぉー けっこう感心じゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきあにきーってベソくてたくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かいてねぇ！全然かいてねぇぞ、これっぽっちも！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しーっ！ミオ姉が起きちまうだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:58.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ごめん…でも、なんでこんな時間に寝てるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,夜に働きに行ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:05.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酒井様の陣、いつ戦になるかわからねぇから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:09.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひと晩じゅう誰かが起きてて、その世話がいるんだってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,夜のほうが賃金がいいし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉は働きがいいから、食いモンも貰えるんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから昼間は寝かせてやらねぇと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:23.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へぇー、お前もけっこう感心だな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！どっか行くのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:31.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ 戦場を避けて通る道がないかと思ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょいと行ってくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:38.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戻らなかったら獣道でもなんでも見つけたと思っとくれ　じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ？連れじゃなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ときどき会うんだ 妙な坊さんでさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また戦になんのかなー…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここも危ねぇな…くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:02.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,国境における酒井の陣には、未だ動きはなく 膠着状態が続いております
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:07.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このまま続くのであれば、新たに兵糧を送らねばならぬかと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その程度の蓄えはあろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁ…ただ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうひと月近く雨がございませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この時期、ここまで降らぬのは珍しきことなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,万が一の備えは必要かと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:29.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が領土において共作などはありえん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうでございましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酒井殿のことに、此度の日照り続き
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それに、今年は山崩れもございました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:47.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まるで…かつてのこの国に戻ったような
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何が言いたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:54.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしどもは、国ごと小さないしずえひとつの上に乗っていることを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お忘れなきようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつ崩れてもおかしくはありませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酒井ごとき小国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:09.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早々に片を付けるよう申し伝えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:09.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せーいせいせいせーい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぞーいぞいぞいぞーい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:34.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せーいせいせいせーい！ぐばぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたたち！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,笑ってないで手伝わなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸、具合はどう？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ熱い…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ 今夜、薬もらってくる！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:05.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酒井様の陣ならきっとあると思うから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃ、仕事行ってくるね！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！もうちょっとしたら夕飯だってさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:29.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤い花つんで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:35.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人にあげよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:42.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人の髪に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:02.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱり安全な道は、お前さんたち獣のほうが知ってるねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつはいい場所だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？こんなとこで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,薬？大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら、すぐに煎じて…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:57.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,不思議ね…なんだか見えてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずっと奥のほうまで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見えてるよ　魂の色が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、勝手に出歩くなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,びっくりするだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,魂の色？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん  おいらもよくわかんねぇけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:15.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きてるモンの魂がいろんな色で見えるんだってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:20.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人だけじゃないぜ？草とか木とか獣とか  あやかしなんか一発でわかっちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっとすげー汚い色してんだろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:27.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そう…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:38.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もしかして、姉ちゃんの歌が聞きたいんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:43.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、姉ちゃんの歌はうるさくないみたいなんだよなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ！姉ちゃんの歌聞いてれば、音に慣れるかも！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今のままじゃ、穴ぐらに籠もった獣みたいなもんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:56.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんの歌で穴から引っ張り出してくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:17:00.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の歌、そんな大層なもんじゃないと思うけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:13.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤い花つんで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:18.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,の人にあげよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:24.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人の髪に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:30.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この花さしてあげよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あら、お坊さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,抜け道、見つかんなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:43.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや  ちょいとばかり、いい話と悪い話を持ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へぇ、そんないい土地があったのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:53.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あそこなら、戦があったってそうそう焼け出されることはないだろうよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちとばかし舐めてみたが、土も悪くなさそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉、行こうぜ！そこに住もう！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,う…うん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,喜ぶのは早いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:07.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,実はその土地には大家がいるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大家？いま空き地だって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:11.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神さ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:17.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありゃ相当だよ うかつに手を出すのは剣呑だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神って、化け物か？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:26.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ  ただのあやかしなんかよりよっぽど強いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そう…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:31.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい、あにき！まさか鬼神退治に行くつもりか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待てよ！そんな足じゃ無理だって！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのつもりで話したところはあるにせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まさか怪我も治らないうちにとは思わなかったかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せっかちだね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:50.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！あにきのこと頼むぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私も…頑張ってみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:11.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,危なっかしいねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え、敵の陣でも動くって…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酒井様の陣と敵の陣と掛け持ちってことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん、今夜からでも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無理だってそんなの！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだよ、今だって大変なんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:28.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも、新しいところに移るならちゃんと準備しなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,土地だけあってもしょうがないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:38.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫！戦でたくさんなくしたぶん、戦から取り戻すだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:44.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さ、そうと決まったらたっぷり寝とかないと！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それじゃ、おやすみ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉、こうと決めたら頑固だからなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも、酒井様の敵陣には荒くれ者が多いって聞くし…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よし！おいらがついてってやるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:01.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前が？だったら俺も…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:05.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメダメ、お前はみんなの面倒見なきゃだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫、あんまり大変そうだったらやめさせる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっか…頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦から取り戻す…か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:19.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいじゃねえか おいらたちだって、侍から取ってやればいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ったく、いつまで睨めっこしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これじゃ手柄の立てようがねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:33.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったくだ こんなド田舎じゃあ、糞以外にすることねぇや
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:34.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お兄さんたち
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,働かせてほしいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれー、ミオ姉どこだ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかるだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫かい？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだやめといたほうがいいんじゃないかねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっちか！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:33.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今さね！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…お前さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,憂鬱が風に散らばり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:48.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,吹き溜まって影になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:55.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,僕らの足音は　無用を饒舌に諭す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:02.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,君の瞳の深さを覗き見て狼狽える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:08.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,望みなどあったでしょうか　この行き先には
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:12.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戯けて笑うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この道が暗いから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:22.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,灯りを灯すのに　僕がいるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:25.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さよならごっこは慣れたもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも手を振ったら泣いちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:35.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,僕らの真っ赤な悲しみが 暮れる 暮れる そして夜が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:38.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,当たり前にやってくる明日なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.87,0:23:41.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きたいなんて言わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:48.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よせばいいのに夢見てしまう 未来 未来 君のせいなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:59.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,"Yocho"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. \NI'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up \NAh... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up \NAh... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. \NI'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,#5 The story of the Moriko Song, part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Still too noisy for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so quiet here it creeps me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the most shocking sense \Nthat Hyakkimaru had so far recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It reverberated relentlessly in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew not how to select which of \Nthe innumerable sounds to listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru drowned in the flood of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe we should give up on \Ngoing after the next monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The reward is handsome, \Nbut you're just not fit for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The bird monster! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, don't worry about the sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was you two? What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, snap out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, his ears eh? Good for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten weaker now that he can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he got beat up by that ghoul \Nthat even you could kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be all right, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten past the worst of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use some medicine, \Nif only we had any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go run and find some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a big town across the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not. I heard \Nthere's a war brewing. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the Sakai clan, \Nwho rules this area, betrayed an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The 2 armies have their swords drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For strangers like us to go near them now \Nwould be suicidal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I turned back \Nand came across you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it, why do samurai \Nlike to fight so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, that was too loud, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, now. Your wounds will open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a wounded beast \Nhiding in his cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear this? This is a human's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The other sounds are the creatures \Nin the woods, the fire, and the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To come out of your cave \Nand live in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hurt. Don't force him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs time to get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What a gentle voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't eat this tough meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the red flower
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In her hair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It blooms and sways
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be in the water. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, hang on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen him so weak before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be because of his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's also regained many things \Nfrom the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's having trouble adjusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are some old rags, but they're clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thanks. \N-Mio, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive us for causing you \Nso much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Please stay until he's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. There are lots of people here \Nlike your big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy, say hello kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a terrible war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost our houses and everything we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all live together here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So none of them have dads or moms?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. But they're all wonderful children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We make do somehow, \Neven though they're all young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis Mio, you're still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, out you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis Mio, you better get some sleep \Nwhile you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch over the hurt guy, \Nso you go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need anything, ask Takebo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up. I made breakfast \Nso eat it before you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some for you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato gruel. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, you watch over your guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit here \Nand do nothing in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me work \Nfor how much you feed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good guy, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you cried like a baby \Nover your guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not! Not even a drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh, you'll wake Sis Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but why is she sleeping now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she works during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sakai army can't say \Nwhen the war might start up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So somebody has to serve them \Nall through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the pay is better \Nduring the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis Mio works hard, \Nso she even gets food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to let her sleep \Nduring the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pretty good guy too, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you off to, Priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to look for a path \Nwhere we can avoid the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be gone long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I don't return, it means I've found \Nsome little path to sneak out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He's not with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We just meet sometimes. He's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's going to be \Nanother war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't stay here either. Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakai's army at the border \Nhasn't made a move. It's a deadlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If this lasts any longer, \Nwe'll have to send more provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We must have enough for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't rained for almost a month now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uncommon to be so dry \Nduring this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We should store up, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no bad harvests on my land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble with Lord Sakai, \Nand now this drought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a landslide this year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we've gone back to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You, I, this domain. \NWe all sit atop a small cornerstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It could crumble and fall any day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell with Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Take care of matters quickly. \N-Yes, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Swish, swish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop giggling and help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you some medicine tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Lord Sakai's army has some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going to work then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Supper will be ready in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a red flower
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To give to her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In her hair
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You creatures know the safe paths \Nbetter than us humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Medicine? Don't worry, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll brew it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange. It feels like you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Down deep inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He can. He sees the color of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you leave like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Color of the soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't get it very much either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can see the colors \Nof the souls of living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just people. Grass, trees, animals. \NHe can find ghouls easily, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they've got a really gross color.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he wants to hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like your song doesn't bother him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! If he listens to you sing, \Nhe'll get used to sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like a hurt beast \Nin a cave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw him out of it with your song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My song isn't that great...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a red flower
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To give to her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In her hair
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put the flower
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No paths out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I have some good news \Nand some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound like a great place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be safe there even if a war starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I licked the soil, and it seemed good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sis Mio. Let's live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Something already owns that land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said it was a vacant lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something \Nwe want to mess with lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, a ghoul?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way stronger than \Njust any old ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not going out there \Nto get it, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you can't with that injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I told you knowing you'd go there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd go \Nbefore your wounds are healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest, take care of him for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try harder, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We really must watch over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to work for the enemy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, you're going to work \Nfor both sides?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, starting tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's hard enough on you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need to get ready \Nto move to the new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't live on an empty lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. War took a lot from us, \Nso let's get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis Mio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I should rest up while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis Mio's really stubborn \Nwhen she wants to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard the enemy is pretty rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You? Then I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you must stay with the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, if things get too tough, \NI'll make her quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them back from war, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that. \NWe'll take from the samurai, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are we going to sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make a name for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nothing to do here but take a dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd Mio go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You should wait until you've healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, your voice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish \Nindifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes, \NI lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope \Nin the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade... \Nuntil night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.87,0:23:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming \Nof a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yocho"
